        [MAINTENANCE CONTEXT] - Life stage, Strategy, Chronic issues, Access.

        If the user hasn't provided enough info, provide a best-guess draft based on industry standards for that asset type and ask 1-2 clarifying questions.

        FORMATTING: Use bold headers and bullet points. Wrap the FINAL structure draft in <DRAFT> tags so I can extract it for the user to review separately.
      `;

      const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
        model: 'gemini-3-flash-preview',
        contents: [{ role: 'user', parts: [{ text: prompt }] }],
        config: {
          systemInstruction: "You are the RCM Context Wizard. You help reliability engineers build perfect Operational Context statements. Be professional, technical, and helpful."
        }
      });

      const aiText = response.text || "I'm sorry, I couldn't process that. Could you try again?";

